These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, milk, almond-milk, iced-tea, water, mirinda
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, japanese, brazilian, argentine, american, indian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, sailing, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo, weightlifting, tennis
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, taxi, bus, boat, skateboard, car, helicopter
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is the brazilian##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the colombian is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the indonesian is on the right of the indian##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the argentine##1
 8. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the helicopter and the american##2
 9. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
10. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is rugby is the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the japanese##1
14. the american is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person driving the car is on the left of the indian##1
16. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking water##1
17. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the japanese##1
18. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the argentine##1
19. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | water        | iced-tea | milk      | almond-milk     | hot-chocolate      | mirinda     |
| Nationality   | colombian | brazilian         | indian   | indonesian | american    | argentine | japanese |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | water-polo | rugby | sailing | tennis  | weightlifting  | lacrosse    |
| Transport     | skateboard  | car         | airplane     | taxi    | bus | boat     | helicopter     |

