 8. the fan of salsa is the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the fan of funk is between the fan of d&b and the person eating blueberry##2
11. the fan of trance is the person eating plum##1
12. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of country##1
13. the fan of blues is between the person eating blueberry and the fan of country##2
14. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the train##1
16. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
17. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
18. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating apple##1
